{"tid":1304482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地班人究竟知唔知乜野係連儂牆？","createTime":"2019-07-10T15:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T02:03:39.000Z","uid":19609,"like":2190,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":115,"replies":[{"pid":"b7cee9518b9b0ced814caef6b2867bd291b5ebd1","tid":1304482,"uid":19609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:27:39.000Z","msg":"連儂牆原指於捷克首都布拉格的一幅滿布塗鴉的牆壁，1980年The Beatles樂隊成員約翰連儂（John Lennon)被槍殺後，有人在牆上畫下約翰連儂畫像及他創作的歌詞，之後就有人開始效法，在牆上留下約翰連儂詞作。80年代後期，民主運動席捲東歐，年青人透過約翰連儂的歌詞，表達對和平、自由的渴求，亦開始對共產政府的極權統治發聲。連儂牆上的塗鴉亦開始不限於與約翰連儂有關。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">捷克當局一度用油漆遮蓋塗鴉，但不久又鋪上了群眾的一筆一劃</span></strong></span>。隨著共產政權瓦解，連儂牆變成自由表達的勝地。連儂牆有個不成文規定，只要有顏料在手，就可以在前人繪畫的塗鴉上，加上自己的作品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">連儂牆存在既意義唔在於實體，而係精神上既存在。本身都預佢拆預佢撕。只要拆一貼十就可以<br />\n<br />\n因為守住一幅牆忘記左抗爭既本意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n守住一幅牆就可以有真普選？ 訓醒未？<br />\n<br />\n當初講好Be water 你地 Be 左去邊？</span>"},{"pid":"4cd3f4897d1351add0da79df3f0736b8e4e88cb0","tid":1304482,"uid":213379,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:28:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">請 停 止 濫 開 有 關 連 儂 牆 同 抵 制 T V B 既 P O S T</span></span><br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304231\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304231</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"38d13ebc3d36b8d8bd6650814ef3b9a057ae7860","tid":1304482,"uid":165336,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:28:25.000Z","msg":"[廢老肆虐]請全線連儂牆變陣<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1303617\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1303617</a>"},{"pid":"43bfff1d2fd8e48af0910f8c91da695d99887a17","tid":1304482,"uid":89627,"like":364,"dislike":4,"score":360,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MJxiLcr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMJxiLcr.png&h=5f705ff4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e07a6668fbb136032966d8738db6c9564fa7d3e4","tid":1304482,"uid":21545,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:28:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab491259098a3b6c3293f775ab2f9b00d9852303","tid":1304482,"uid":514,"like":328,"dislike":2,"score":326,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:30:06.000Z","msg":"雨革就係輸在死守一個地方<br />\n而家又點解要守連儂牆？<br />\n連儂牆最重要係佢嘅精神。有呢個精神嘅人，去到邊，嗰度就係連儂牆<br />\n<br />\nBe water<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5980ec75f0e6f79c001028c1fd91abecb70e4833","tid":1304482,"uid":89627,"like":100,"dislike":0,"score":100,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:31:42.000Z","msg":"成個運動嘅行動主旨係 Be water! My friend<br />\n唔係鼓吹失敗主義，只係想啲手足（尤其係旺角黑夜同埋今晚油塘）唔好諗住死守。<br />\n<br />\n死守呢個行動策略，已經係五年前證明咗係唔work<br />\n所以Be water, my friend!"},{"pid":"f2974863fe57e0e0322554a523e9db7cac7b667a","tid":1304482,"uid":19609,"like":100,"dislike":1,"score":99,"quote":{"pid":"ab491259098a3b6c3293f775ab2f9b00d9852303","tid":1304482,"uid":514,"like":328,"dislike":2,"score":326,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:30:06.000Z","msg":"雨革就係輸在死守一個地方<br />\n而家又點解要守連儂牆？<br />\n連儂牆最重要係佢嘅精神。有呢個精神嘅人，去到邊，嗰度就係連儂牆<br />\n<br />\nBe water<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:31:57.000Z","msg":"好撚同意 只要植左入腦 邊到都係連儂場<br />\n<br />\n你睇下東方昇？ 雖然假膠但點出左精髓"},{"pid":"4f35a799a5bebecb8c25f6a4b02fac15bca6b0fa","tid":1304482,"uid":53803,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:32:22.000Z","msg":"哪裡有香港人 哪裡就有連儂牆<br />\n基本上你行街周圍噴都得<br />\n唔而要拘泥於某一個位<br />\n今日係TG見到人當壁佈版咁整<br />\n可能真係誤會左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11a0ae2d4c1f1d6adbe2882b71d2cc4dd9129c2","tid":1304482,"uid":514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:33:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3501468424acc666856ef4ee61c60940d180de67","tid":1304482,"uid":19609,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:36:08.000Z","msg":"係唔係想保住d 連儂牆，等十年廿年後起個六四展覽館咁既野？  <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">識衝，更加要識退</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n識得退落黎先係最難"},{"pid":"738a7777ef56e596a59e466468355c2f8815a60d","tid":1304482,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一早講左 be water 只係口號啦     <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc8a0a7aebe91a09e4938132b9a0ff61a727c64","tid":1304482,"uid":147643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e7758b7775ec0c9f57a555f57bc97a7d61c791","tid":1304482,"uid":91842,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:03:14.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34524bbcd5e41c2147c843df705cac97be06b96a","tid":1304482,"uid":240534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:55:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a74f4d7075bc755bfaafc3fe4f97198b19b4dd2b","tid":1304482,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:59:32.000Z","msg":"形式主義民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f968d724805a1af6b096a2367602de668fc34f","tid":1304482,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:03:19.000Z","msg":"唔守唔硬碰冇問題，但我唔撚明點解